						               													<description>In the &amp;quot;SD&amp;quot; World, humans and Mobile Suits lived peacefully side by side. Peace would not last long as Devil Gundam arrived and cast a shadow upon the land. King Levir of the LeCroix dynasty gave the task of defeating the enemy to his Gundam Knights. The Gundam Knights departed immediately to the mountainous frontier of the LaCroix Kingdom to turn back Devil Gundam and his forces.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this strategic board game based on the highly successful SD Gundam series, players will each assume the role of a Gundam Knight protecting the LaCroix Kingdom. Players will roll dice to move on the grid based board and use weapon and attack cards to overpower and defeat the enemies, and Devil Gundam, to save the LaCroix Kingdom!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SD Gundam: LaCroix Heroes has two game modes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Mode One: The Three Legendary Sacred Shrines. In this game mode, players will be battling the forces of Devil Gundam who have seized control of the Legendary Sacred Shrines. In order to defeat Satan Gundam, you must journey to the Shrines, defeat the enemies within, collect the Sacred Treasure from each shrine (Shield of Power, Armor of Power, and the Sword of Fire) in order to be powerful enough to defeat Devil Gundam.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Mode Two: Castle of Devil Gundam. The Knight Gundams, having reached the fortress of the enemy, with the Three Sacred Treasures in hand, must penetrate and search the Castle to find the Sacred Stone Tablet with the spell that will imbue the Sacred Treasures with their legendary power, allowing the players to try and defeat Devil Gundam. But will victory prove so easy?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
